{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d118482447","title":"大字报：“我们要扩大民主”","origin":"《南开大学右派反动言论选辑(第二集)》(南开大学社会主义思想教育教研组，1957.10)。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"45b62de413","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"d118482447"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"31303e81fc","name":"杨福徵"},{"id":"8176da31cf","name":"靳健"},{"id":"e920af9be9","name":"蔡戴熙"},{"id":"f2840d39f9","name":"南开大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ecdc69dccc","type":"title","text":"大字报：“我们要扩大民主”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"fe1861a2d2","type":"authors","text":"南开大学蔡戴熙靳健杨福徵","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"420559c64e","type":"subtitle","text":"[蔡戴熙、靳健、杨福徵：南开大学物理系助教研究生]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"5927eba190","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）“我们要扩大民主”：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"c854a520bd","type":"paragraph","text":"1、胡风是不是反革命？据现有的材料不足以证明为反革命。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"d3972a9b29","type":"paragraph","text":"2、对高饶事件，我们知道的更少，这样我们也没有办法确定是不是反革命？","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"39d826f244","type":"paragraph","text":"3、反对搞思想工作中“以力服人”粗暴办法教育人们！不要把抱有“正流”观念不同见解的人，看作异教徒，而施以各种形式的压力。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"b1e2ffaea4","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）“呜呼！大失所望”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"89cd87502e","type":"paragraph","text":"1、呜呼！大失所望！党委的整风计划在那里？决定在那里？","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"9c8204af46","type":"paragraph","text":"2、我们要重新对肃反进行估价。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"7a22f6de5d","type":"paragraph","text":"3、学生会应真正的代表同学们的意见。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"b0dbebae6b","type":"paragraph","text":"4、立即召开全校师生职工大会，保证言论自由，决不报复打击。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"0579b94f68","type":"paragraph","text":"5、立刻开辟大礼堂作为自由讲坛。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"844b7315b3","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）答数四的几位同学","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"bb72785666","type":"paragraph","text":"①关于“高饶”问题的进一步阐述：","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"737c9c1eb5","type":"paragraph","text":"要求对这一事件作进一步说明，怎能说是命令党这样或那样呢？","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"f3b00ce230","type":"paragraph","text":"正如物一同学所指的那样党和行政，是有区别的，党内的事情不应和行政的事情混为一谈，党可以处分一个党员（开除党籍）但是作为一个公民，而且过去是领导人被定罪被解除行政职务难道这只是党内的事情吗？另外一些公民就不能过问吗？过问了就定一个命令党“这样那样”的罪吗？","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"f50ed513ce","type":"paragraph","text":"②关于北大校友来校问题","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"2af68af21b","type":"paragraph","text":"对这一事件看法是一个公民的权利你们无权干涉，至于说北大校友来校这和我们有什么关系？","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"5e37f69657","type":"paragraph","text":"③我校的领导没有“以力服人”的事吗？你们四年来遇到的尽是“以理服人”吗？可举的例子太多啦，顾笔写来；","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"d9aa4b498d","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）思想改造时刚回国的满腔热情的某教授（是个博士学位的获得者）由于工作不细致方式粗暴，弄的精神失常，到现在不能开课这不是“以力服人”吗？","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"ab3373785f","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）肃反中我班班长被一口咬定是反革命分子，制造一些虚假的罪名（他曾检举别人的材料，结果被肃委会压下，反扣假检举大帽）结果证明斗错了。是不是“以力服人”？","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"8294b99a4d","type":"paragraph","text":"物理系助教及研究室","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"},{"id":"0a61fbe4af","type":"paragraph","text":"曹贤康 黄学崇 徐元上 谭华铮 蔡戴熙 杨福徵靳健 钱灿圭","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447"}],"page":{"id":"a6743651ae","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d118482447","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}